  "algorithm": "per band, draw unique (a, b) operand tuples from random.Random(seed + ':' + band_id) uniform in the declared inclusive ranges, rejecting duplicate tuples, until n_tasks tuples exist; assign tuples to the predeclared task_ids in draw order",
